{"tid":1150571,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"【高峰過後會退，煙花開過便散】咁大個人都仲係學唔識接受空虛","createTime":"2019-05-12T02:58:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T03:01:38.000Z","uid":200019,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"81bb51d297ad4ed18a8b0a21018e713953a8e942","tid":1150571,"uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T02:58:00.000Z","msg":"小弟依家做緊嘅職業會接觸好多人<br />\n三十幾歲就會急流勇退<br />\n<br />\n未高峰就要離開<br />\n<br />\n身邊嘅同事一年換一班<br />\n未成為朋友就要永別<br />\n<br />\n我覺得世界好空虛<br />\n人又需唔要追求永恒<br />\n<br />\n越諗越覺得世界最後都只會淨返我一個<br />\n真係覺得做我好寂寞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"098c8d6243c93bd6d17d0dc72cc37a92d5dc7044","tid":1150571,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T02:59:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1df6045b9aa798d769f9da95c40f22d676c1a09f","tid":1150571,"uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"098c8d6243c93bd6d17d0dc72cc37a92d5dc7044","tid":1150571,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T02:59:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T03:01:38.000Z","msg":"你唔覺咩？"}]}